The Immortals of Dark Pawns are those who have proven themselves worthy of
godhood through great deeds, contributions to the world, or by remorting and
earning a place among the divine.

The gods are a mysterious lot, preferring to remain obfuscated and mysterious
to the mortal population. It is known that they do speak to some mortals,
however.

Immortals:

  Serapis
  Orodreth
  Frontline
  Aralius
  Hulk
  Doragar
